{
  "text": "The algorithm can be applied to different evaluations. For example (ok(2), ok(1), , wrong [CITATION_1] , wrong(2)) or (ok, known, ?, wrong). If the user evaluates a document as ok all the parameters that are part of the document (keywords, author, year,…) will be incremented/included in the model for this type of evaluation.",
